headline: BofA lists 16 stock opportunities away from AI
summary: Investing.com -- Bank of America analysts said investor enthusiasm around artificial intelligence has left a range of attractively valued companies overlooked, identifying 16 “non-AI” opportunities that combine solid earnings momentum with discounted valuations.
